title: The Trender Of The Zeit 11/11: NFL, Germany, Cracker Barrel, Inflation, Astroworld, Debra Messing

description:
In this edition of The Trender of the Zeit, Jack and Miles discuss NFL news, Germany's COVID crisis, 'millenials' trying Cracker Barrel for the first time, the inflation surge, the 'demonological' analysis of the Astroworld, and Deborah Messing > Nicole Kidman as Lucille Ball according to Twitter.
